<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<title>Activation Mail</title>
		<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

		<style>
			body { margin: 0; padding: 0; min-width: 100%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.5; background-color: #FAFAFA; color: #2D333A; }
			a { color: #2D333A; text-decoration: none; }
			h1 { font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.25; margin: 0 auto 15px auto; text-align: center; }
			p { margin: 0 auto 24px auto; }
			table td { vertical-align: top; }
			.footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; color: #2D333A; }
			.footer > p > a { text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; color: #2D333A; }
			.email-wrapper { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }
			.email-header { background-color: #0070F3; padding: 24px; color: #FAFAFA; }
			.email-body { padding: 24px; background-color: #FAFAFA; }
			.email-footer { background-color: #0070F3; padding: 24px; color: #FAFAFA; }
			.button { display: inline-block; background-color: #0070F3; color: #FAFAFA; font-size: 1em; font-weight: 700; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 4px; }
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="email-wrapper">
			<div class="email-header">
				<h1>Welcome to Company Name</h1>
			</div>
			<div class="email-body">
				<p>Hello <%=user.name %>,</p>
				<p>Thank you for Registrering with us. To Activate your account, Please use the following Activation Code:</p>
				<h2><%= activationCode %></h2>
				<p>Please enter this code on the activation page withing the next 5 minutes...!</p>
				<p>if you did not register for an account, please ignore this email.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="email-footer">
				<p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact the admin at <a href="mailto:ellis0078@gmail.com">Ellis Sanjay Tarmaster</a></p>
			</div>
			<div class="footer">
				<p>&copy; 2024 Company name. All rights reserved.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>